Description:
Vcare is a Corporate group from Chennai & they are into slimming & beauty. I met them in Mumbai along with Marcia as we got an inquiry from them regarding their requirement for InBody 270. 

I had a meeting with the Director of the company and he was interested in purchasing 11 units of InBody 270. We finally had a negotiation and closed the pricing at USD $5194 per units for InBody 270 subject to a single order for 11 units of InBody 270.

Deal Name: Golds Gym (Fit & Free Fitness Solutions Pvt Ltd)-
Description: This is a Golds Gym franchise from Thirssur Kerala. I have finalized the order in the Golds Gym convention which took place in Feb, 2016 in Sri Lanka. The order is for one unit of InBody 270 along with BSM 170B.

Received this inquiry from Marcia as it was posted on InBody HQ website. Had a decision with the customer and he is interested in InBody 270 for his clinic. Since he has limited budget he wants to go from InBody 270 only.

Have shared with him all the relevant product information along with the price quotation. He will get back to me shortly with his decision.

Met Dr. Sreejoy Patnaik last year in Apollo Hospital, Delhi during a Bariatric Surgery Seminar. Got a call from him few days back regarding their requirement for InBody. Since Cuttack is a T3 city they were initially willing to go for InBody 120, however did manage to convince them to atleast by InBody 270 and have finalised the order for the same.

Got this inquiry today on InBody India website. After having a telephonic conversation with the customer, got to know that she is coming up with a Diet clinic of her own and requires InBody for her centre. She has inquired about InBody 370 / InBody 570 & InBody 770. I have provided her with all the detailed information of all these 3 products along with the pricing of the same. 

She has mentioned that she will be discussing with her husband & will get back to me. I personally feel that she might be settling down for InBody 370. However, since the lead is on very initially stage so I wont comment but I will try to convince her to settle down for atleast InBody 570.

Got this inquiry on InBody India website and after having telephonic discussion with Mr. Felipe Alvares got to know that he is coming up with a Gym in Goa and they require InBody 270 for their centre. Have provided him with all the product detailing along with the prices. 

Order to be expected by mid June, 2016

Golds Gym franchise taken by Mr. Salim Memon. He will be opening his centre in Vasai suburb in Mumbai & I had a telephonic discussion with Mr. Salim and discussed about his requirement. 

He is planning to meet me in Mumbai on 31st and would like to have a discussion with me. Will be going for InBody 270.

Golds Gym franchise owner for Indore city. Mr. Aman Raj Verma is the franchise owner for upcoming Golds Gym in Indore. I have had been in discussion with him from last 6 months and due to delay in construction work at the site the opening date got extended.

He is now planning to open the centre by mid June. He will be going for InBody 270

Met Mr. Chopra yesterday at Physique Global city tour in Delhi as he attended the event. He is basically an advocate and is running a consultation company. However, he is coming up with a Gym in East Delhi and is interested in purchasing InBody device. 

He will be calling me this week for a meeting and will decide on which InBody model to purchase for his centre.

Met Mr. Vedula Charki at Physique Global city tour in Hyderabad. He attended the event and is coming up with a Gym by August 2016. He showed interest in InBody devices after having a demonstration there & will decided for a model within a budget range of Rs. 4,50,000/- 

Will have a telephonic discussion with him next week & will proceed further with his requirement.

Ms. Monisha is a Nutritionist who is working at K.S. Medical Academy, Mangalore which is a city in Karnataka. She is setting up her own clinic and wants to purchase a portable model which she can move around for conducting events in the city. I have briefed her about IB 120 and have provided her with all the details. She will get back to me shortly.

Mr. Satish Paryada is the Master Franchise of Gethins Gym for South India. To give a brief detail on the Gethins Gym, I got in touch with Mr. Jag Chima who is the brain child along with Kris Gethin who is a Celebrity Trainer in India at BodyPower Expo in 2015. After that I developed great association with Mr. Jag Chima & got InBody 270 approved after giving a demo to Kris Gethin & Jag Chima. 

Have installed InBody 270 at their first centre in April at Banjara Hills. Meanwhile, during this Physique Global tour I have had a discussion with Mr. Jag Chima and have emphasised on procuring InBody 570. While, Mr. Chima is quite interested in InBody 570, he has mentioned that the final approval will come from Mr. Satish Paryada who is the master franchise for Gethins Gym in South India. 

I am meeting Mr. Jag Chima in Mumbai on 8th June, 2016 during my upcoming business trip & will get to know their decision on the same.

Met the concerned person Mr. Pradeep from F 45 at Physique Global Tour in Bangalore and he showed interest in InBody devices. He has asked me to send him the details along with the pricing of all the different InBody variants which are appropriate for Fitness centre. 

Upon going through the same, he will make a decision on the same.

Apple Fitness is another upcoming Corporate Fitness chain which has got 3 centres in Bangalore and they are coming up with 3 more centers within next one year. Mr. Kiran is the owner of this brand and I met him at the Physique Global City tour in Bangalore as he attended the seminar. He is using InBody 230 previously and now wants to purchase InBody 270 for his upcoming centre. 

Have provided him with all the information regarding InBody 270 along with the pricing.

Made a cold call to Mr. Tanmay Mishra as we got an inquiry on our website. He is coming up with a fitness center & wanted to know about InBody 230 & InBody 270. I have briefed him about InBody 270 and provided him all the relevant details along with the quotation for InBody 270. He will get back to me shortly after discussing with his team.

Deal Name: Occupational Health Centre, HeroMotor Corp. Ltd.-
Description: HereMotoCorp is a Corporate organisation & Dr. Rajat Kumar Saha is incharge for their Health Center. They are interested in purchasing our InBody BCA device. He visited our office & took demonstration for InBody 270 and liked the machine. However, since they have a budget of Rs. 4,00,000/- for BCA device we had no option but to quote InBody 270 only. However, we have currently provided them with the final price of Rs. 4,75,000/- and Dr. Rajat has informed that he will get back to us after getting approval from hire management.

This is a Gym in Lovely Professional University in Phagwara, Punjab. They have been using InBody 170 from last couple of years. Now they want to upgrade to InBody 270 & have inquired about the same. Karn got a call from the customer & I took a follow for the same. They wanted details about InBody 270 along with the pricing. Have shared all the details with them.
Mr. Anil is coming up with a Golds Gym franchise in Pune. Have provided him with the product details along with Golds Gym Corporate pricing. He will be getting back to me shortly.
Got this inquiry on our website & had a communication with the customer. However, due to lack of budget the customer rejected to go for InBody BCA device.
Dr. Rucha Mehta is an endocrinologist and inquired about InBody BCA devices. However, due to her budget which was way too long as Rs. 1,00,000/- we could not even offer her InBody 120.

Got this lead forwarded by Marcia. Had a word with Mr. Imran Bajaj who is owner of the Gym. After having a telephonic discussion with him, he has requested to send the quotation for InBody 270 along with the product catalog. Upon going through the same he will get back to me.

Since he is beginning weight lost management program at this centre, he is interested in purchasing a BCA device. He has requested for product catalog and pricing for the same & he will get back to me after sometime.

Mr. Khatib Rehman is coming up with a Golds Gym in Bhuwnaeshwar, Odisha and he plans to launch the center in August. He will be going for InBody 270 & will place the order once he is ready for his centre's pre-sales in the beginning of August.

Deal Name: Sports Authority of India - Indian Badiminton Team-
Description: Got inquiry from Dr. Kiran who is a Physiotherapist in Indian Badminton team. They are interested in purchasing InBody BCA device for their Badminton team. While, I tried really hard to convince them to go for InBody 570 as it is the best suited InBody model for their department, but since the budget allocated by the Government is not more than Rs. 5,50,000/- they had no option but to settle down for InBody 270. However, Dr. Kiran has mentioned that may be in next year budget they can put InBody 570 in their budget and acquire the device.

This is an inquiry forwarded by Marcia. Talwalkars is a Corporate Chain of Gyms in India and few of their centers are already using InBody devices. Mr. Madhukar Talwalkar is the owner of the Gym chain & myself & Marcia have met him as well. Meanwhile, since their Gyms are low budget Gyms, few of the centers opt for Body Composition Analysers.

However, Mr. Harish Kumar is the Operations Manager for South India centers and he is interested in purchasing InBody 270 for his Bangalore centre. Had a telephonic conversation with him & he has requested me to send quotation for InBody 270 along with product catalogs and specifications.
Order finalised with Mr. Sunil Madane who is the owner of Endurance Fitness. They are coming up with another Gym and have decided to go for InBody 270 for their centre.

We have been working on Apollo Group of Hospitals from a long time & proposed InBody 370 for their multiple centers spread across PAN India. Have provided several demo to them along with various meetings with the management in the past,I am hereby glad to inform you all that we have got InBody 370 approved & have got the order from their Nashik, Maharashtra hospital today. This is a good start for us when it comes to Apollo Hospitals & will definitely open doors for us selling more InBody 370's in their other hospitals / clinics across India.

Special credit goes to Karn for his constant support & efforts working closely with Apollo Group of Hospitals, providing them with best possible services along with product detailing & information. This order is a perfect example of team work & I would like to thank Karn for all his efforts & support for this order from Apollo Group of hospitals.
